txt.en: Sûhalar warriors can be found along the Rammas.\n\nYou should defeat Sûhalar warriors on top of the Rammas.
'There are many Easterlings upon the Out-wall. You should defeat as many as you can so that we may retake the Rammas with haste.'
Sûhalar warriors can be found along the Rammas.\n\nYou should defeat Sûhalar warriors on top of the Rammas.
Easterlings have invaded the northern Rammas and it is up to you to see them off the Out-wall.
